PrecisTransfer to the Province of Alberta of the administration and control over a total of some 2,391.92 hectares of land situate on BLOOD INDIAN RESERVE NO. 148, as well as certain rights of access over a total of some 44.5 miles of road or trails, all of which are required for the purposes of an irrigation development project, in lieu of such taking by the Province without the consent of the owners.
